OL,3,CMan who planned terrorist attack on
OL,4,Cschool detained in mental health
OL,5,Cfacility
OL,7,FA man from Jersey has been detained in
OL,8,Fa mental health institution following
OL,9,Fa hearing at Jersey's Royal Court
OL,10,Fafter pleading guilty to committing
OL,11,Fterrorism and sex offences.
OL,13,F27 year old Daniel McMillan was
OL,14,Farrested last year after police were
OL,15,Falerted by mental health services to
OL,16,Fhis plans to carry out a mass killing
OL,17,Fat Les Quennevais School where he used
OL,18,Fto be a student.
