OL,7,FMcMillan had pleaded guilty to having
OL,8,Fcommitted terrorism offences and
OL,9,Fpossessing prohibited and indecent
OL,10,Fimages of children and unlawful sexual
OL,11,Fintercourse.
OL,13,FOnce the investigation began, it was
OL,14,Ffound that he was in the advanced
OL,15,Fplanning and preparation stages of
OL,16,Fthis attack.
