OL,3,CMan who planned terrorist attack on
OL,4,Cschool detained in mental health
OL,5,Cfacility
OL,7,FMcMillan's planned attack focused on
OL,8,Fcarrying out a mass killing at a
OL,9,Fschool using a home-made flamethrower
OL,10,Fand axe with clothing and accessories
OL,11,Fdesigned to obscure his identity.
OL,13,FHe had learned how to make a
OL,14,Fflamethrower, explosives and chemical
OL,15,Fcompounds online and upon searching
OL,16,Fhis home police found a pressure
OL,17,Fwasher, butane and propane gas
OL,18,Fcannisters, an axe, rope and liquid
OL,19,Fcontainers.
