OL,4,Cschool detained in mental health
OL,5,Cfacility
OL,7,FMcMillan had also revisited the school
OL,8,Fin 2022 to strategise.
OL,10,FDuring the investigation police also
OL,11,Ffound indecent images of children on
OL,12,FMcMillan's devices.
OL,14,FDetective Inspector Paul Ryan said:
OL,15,F"Terrorism offences are extremely rare
OL,16,Fin Jersey. The
OL,18,Frevelation of McMillan's plans, early
OL,19,Fintervention and subsequent conviction
OL,20,Fwere made possible by the joint work
OL,21,Fbetween multiple agencies.
