OL,7,F"We know that details from this case
OL,8,Fmay be particularly alarming but want
OL,9,Fto reassure the community that reports
OL,10,Fof criminality of this nature are
OL,11,Frobustly assessed and investigated.
OL,13,F"As soon as these offences came to
OL,14,Flight, McMillan was arrested and
OL,15,Fremanded in custody whilst the
OL,16,Finvestigation was conducted.
